title.narrative: India National Cyclone Risk Mitigation Project (1)

description.narrative: The Project Development Objection (PDO) of the National Cyclone Risk Mitigation Project (1) (NCRMP-1) is to reduce the vulnerability of coastal communities in Andhra Pradesh and Orissa to cyclone and other hydro meteorological hazards.
